item.description: SoftLayer_Container_Product_Order_SshKeys Datatype Description This object holds all of the ssh key ids that will allow authentication to a single server. Local sshKeyIds An array of SoftLayer_Security_Ssh_Key IDs to assign to a server. Type: array of integers
